business functionalities :
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
main :
-------
- facebook ads spy tool : get ads with all related info (performance, targeting, engagement, media) [adview]
- create and manage (campaigns, target audience, adsets, ads)
- manage facebook page (posts, stories, content)
- manage facebook pixels and conversion 
- manage (create, update, see info) youcan landing page
- dashboard where account managers can make their work


extra : 
